thread.title: Teresa Meza
thread.title_full: Maine Lobster Now reviewed by Teresa Meza

author: Teresa Meza
title: Teresa Meza
text:
Lobsters arrived Saturday morning, as expected, all alive and making happy noises, we iced them and cooked them on Sunday for Lunch adding a little Cajun Flair to it, mushrooms, corn, potatoes, onions and Cajun spices.
Delicious! Birthday Boy was pleasantly surprised! (my husband)
Enjoyed by all!!!
Teresa Meza
Lafayette,Louisiana
